snippet.textDisplay: the only thing i remember with this song is that it was late at night and my then boyfriend was so much passionate about music that he introduced me to this song. he was a musician and he paused the song at every second to explain me about background, artists and everything. i felt so special that night. somebody made so much efforts for me for the first time. i still remember feeling so so special. then in morning we both confessed our feelings for each other. and even though we are not together anymore. whenever i listen to this song i remember the old version of me which was so innocent and i still remember everything he taught me about the instruments, vocal chords, everything about this song.
